items.display_name: Near East Zesty Lemon Quinoa Blend
items.details:
A blend of quinoa & brown rice. With other natural flavors.
Per Serving: 250 Calories; 0.5g Sat Fat--3% (DV); 380mg Sodium--16% (DV); 1g Sugars; 4g Fiber--15% (DV).
Near East Quinoa Blend: Quinoa (pronounced KEEN-wah), is a unique, versatile whole grain with a slightly crunchy texture and a light nutty flavor that is used around the world. A good source of fiber. Contains 5g total fat per serving as prepared. One cup serving contains 29 grams of whole grain. Fair Trade is a global movement that aims to give farmers competitive prices, improved trade terms and incentives to invest in their community and help protect the environment.
Variations: For a creative twist add one of the following to the cooked quinoa: 1/2 cup roasted red peppers and 1 Tablespoon fresh basil; 1/2 cup steamed asparagus; 1/2 cup Gruyere cheese, shredded; 1 teaspoon fresh grated ginger and 1/4 cup silvered almonds (add during simmer); 1 clove minced garlic and 1/4 cup toasted pine nuts (add during simmer); 1/2 cup cooked shrimp, chicken or tofu; In preparation, seasoned broth or stock can be substituted for water.
items.directions: Range Top Directions: 1. In a medium saucepan, bring quinoa/brown rice blend, 1 teaspoon olive oil and 1-3/4 cups water to a boil. 2. Turn heat to a medium boil, add contents of Spice Sack and mix well. 3. Boil gently for 14 to 17 minutes until water is absorbed. 4. Cover; remove from heat. Let stand 5 minutes. Fluff with a fork before serving. Microwave Directions: 1. In round 2-quart microwaveable glass casserole, combine quinoa/brown rice blend, contents of Spice Sack, 1-3/4 cups water, and 1 teaspoon olive oil. 2. Cover; microwave at High for 6 minutes. Mix. 3. Cover; microwave at High for 6 to 10 minutes or until all water is absorbed. 4. Let stand 5 minutes. 5. Fluff lightly with fork before serving. Microwave ovens may vary. Adjust times as needed. High Altitude Preparation: At high altitudes, increase water to 2 cups and cook time by 5 minutes.
items.ingredients: Quinoa, Parboiled Long Grain Brown Rice, Maltodextrin, Olive Oil, Salt, Onions*, Potassium Chloride, Parsley*, Garlic*, Spices, Torula Yeast, Soy Protein, Carrots*, Citric Acid, Autolyzed Yeast Extract, Lemon Oil, Tocopherols For Freshness, Natural Flavors, Vinegar, Corn Starch, Soy Sauce (Soybean, Wheat, Salt), Tomato Powder. *Dried.
